The General Overseer of Mountain of Fire and Miracles Ministries (MFM), Dr. Daniel Olukoya, has appealed to Ni­gerians to be more aggressive in prayers to combat the chal­lenges of the New Year. Describing the New Year 2021 as a ‘Year of the Valley,’ the cleric released 34 prophe­cies to usher in the New Year on Thursday evening. Olukoya, who tagged 2021 as the ‘Year of Restoration and Re­vival’, urged Nigerians during the Church’s annual crossover service, to pray because 2021 would be a year of the valley. ABUJA DOCTOR REVEALS HOW MOST NIGERIA MEN ARE NOW OVERCOMING TERRIBLE BEDROOM PERFORMANCE DUE TO THIS BRILLIANT DISCOVERY. DON'T BE A VICTIM! Olukoya noted that acidic prayers are needed to get de­sirable results because it is a year of the valley “So, the three keys to tack­ling this year of the valley are the presence of God, aggres­sive holiness, and aggressive prayers,” he said. Group Cautions Plateau LGA Workers Against Minimum Wage Protest Fun Seekers Disappointed Over Cancellation Of Activities At National Theatre Some of the prophecies include: “It is a year where serious prayers are needed to confront the fruit of this pan­demic. The pandemic is yield­ing terrible fruits. It is a year of aggressive engagement of the enemies in violent warfare. It is a year of terrible temptations. It is a year of deep distresses that only the balm of Gilead can solve. It is going to be a year of strange rebellion and conspiracy. It is a year where John 10:10 will play out aggres­sively. Unless we pray very well, there will be a breakdown of structures and protest. It is a year of wilderness wander­ing and vagabond. Many will wake up and discover they’ve destroyed their lives. It will be a year of multiple-magnified multiple problems. Anyone who has come from polyga­mous family should pray very well in 2021 because the effect of that polygamous will be hugely dramatised. It is a year of programmed controversies. It is a year that will need to pray against the rage of the